{"tid":749933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[柒警無事]法國總統府職員涉傷人被捕後遭馬克龍解僱","createTime":"2018-07-20T12:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T13:19:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58a851ef09f601e4ebc6a146617664d274c0338e","tid":749933,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"法國警方扣留涉嫌在勞動節遊行中，毆打示威者的總統府職員。檢方表示，該名職員面臨公職人員使用暴力、冒充警員、未經授權使用監控錄像等罪。<br />\n<br />\n總統府表示，總統馬克龍已經將該名職員解僱，其餘三名總統府官員因為向涉嫌打人的職員提供監控錄像而被停職。<br />\n<br />\n總統府發言人日前表示，這名職員奉命觀察遊行時，被認出戴著警察頭盔毆打參與五一遊行的人，明顯超越職權，被停職15天作為懲罰。反對派質疑懲罰太輕，批評政府包庇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408111-20180720.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408111-20180720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3rBK0zhC1nPZNeBCr%2Byu%2BgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0aa79aee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408111-20180720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=318f8d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408111-20180720.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c49650b8e351c3087667d34a7b7cb2bd9f80706f","tid":749933,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51a43a43f7c94a21f6adb24bef49683d0eb1e8b3","tid":749933,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}